original_title: Orleans: We're Still Havin' Fun!: A Live Concert Film
overview: Soft rock stalwarts Orleans light up a warm night in August 2006 with a concert of classic hits, performed by original members Larry Hoppen, Lance Hoppen and John Hall. Tracks include "Love Takes Time," "Still the One" and "Dance with Me.
title: Orleans: We're Still Havin' Fun!: A Live Concert Film
